{"type":"click","text":"Button.vue\n            src/components/ · 添加 loading 状态\n          \n          \n            +2\n            −1\n          \n        \n\n        \n        \n          \n            \n            Before\n          \n          \n          \n            \n            After\n          \n        \n\n        \n        \n          \n          \n            \n            \n              13\n              <template>\n            \n            \n            \n              14\n                <button :class=\"btnClass\">\n            \n            \n            \n              \n            \n            \n            \n              15\n                  <slot />\n            \n            \n              16\n                </button>\n            \n          \n\n          \n          \n\n          \n          \n            \n            \n              13\n              <template>\n            \n            \n            \n              14\n                <button :class=\"btnClass\" :disabled=\"loading\">\n            \n            \n            \n              15\n                  <Loader v-if=\"loading\" class=\"animate-spin\" />\n            \n            \n            \n              16\n                  <slot />\n            \n            \n              17\n                </button>\n            \n          \n        \n\n        \n        \n          \n            \n            应用更改\n          \n          撤销\n          查看全文\n          \n            \n            AI generated · hunk 1/1\n          \n        \n      \n    \n    \n      A. 深邃沉浸型（推荐）\n      深黑底 + 微光晕。左侧删除行渐变红左边框，右侧新增行渐变绿右边框。字符级差异用圆角 pill 高亮。行号低对比度不干扰阅读。顶部 Before/After 标签带色点。","choice":"immersive-sbs","id":null,"timestamp":1776352776609}
